# Railway API Token Rotation - Issue #739

## Context
The RAILWAY_TOKEN GitHub secret used for Deploy to staging pipeline has expired or been revoked.
This blocks all deployments until the token is rotated.

## Manual Steps Required
1. Create new permanent Railway API token: https://railway.com/account/tokens
2. Update GitHub secret: gh secret set RAILWAY_TOKEN --repo alexsiri7/reli
3. Re-run failed CI: gh run rerun 25007185051 --repo alexsiri7/reli

